{"tid":1827661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意咗第二個......","createTime":"2020-01-17T06:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T01:34:14.000Z","uid":64867,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"adefae9fc19a536bc60aee1ea5094d33b2567141","tid":1827661,"uid":64867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:31:16.000Z","msg":"我本身同佢拍緊第6年，佢對我好好，亦都對我做嘅各種決定(進修，出國做嘢之類)等百份百支持，有plan結婚<br />\n<br />\n但係問題係佢屋企好多問題，佢係小六果陣喺大陸落嚟，<br />\n所以有啲家人喺大陸，佢屋企人理財好似有啲問題，成日都家嘈屋閉，雖然佢屋企人對我幾好，但我好厭倦佢屋企成日有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁最近呢我就識咗個嚟香港做嘢嘅日本人，咁大家都志趣相投所以好好傾，亦都開始有啲曖昧，早幾日佢叫我上佢屋企，我跟住佢去到屋企樓下，最終都係無上到去<br />\n<br />\n第二個呢就屋企大部分都係公務員或者軍人，佢喺果邊就自己住，都叫有啲錢咁<br />\n<br />\n其實本身而家呢個對我好好，但好衰唔衰我又對另一個人產生咗好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知點算<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲教下我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92309a602ed12008bb2ce3e84fe62ba8d8fba4a6","tid":1827661,"uid":276054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"臭雞唔好害人"},{"pid":"1bcc3843ee1c42e52132ec72f164659dde3dfe7c","tid":1827661,"uid":263680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"臭雞唔好害人"},{"pid":"d70b802fd5cb4e6342228daec10d68ff4731dea9","tid":1827661,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"if it comes ones <br />\nit comes afterwards <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ad6292be06a964186936faed50bc3f00e07421","tid":1827661,"uid":45324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"你有第3個 pmed<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5323240d6d3790b74e18